node.text:
Want VIP tickets to my fight on September 25? Got one of my Revolut cards?

I’ve partnered with @revolutapp to bring one lucky winner and a friend to London on an all-expenses-paid trip to see the fight and meet me during fight week 🥊 Here’s how you can win:

💥 Comment below with why you want to attend the fight
💥 Tag the friend you would take with you
💥 Like this pic, follow me and @revolutapp 
💥 Buy a glow-in-the-dark AJ card through the Revolut app, if you don’t have one already

You must have an AJ Revolut card to enter. The winner and their friend must be over 18 years old and will be picked on September 2nd, 2021. Open to selected countries. Check the T&Cs for more details. One winner will be selected and they’ll be contacted directly from the @revolutapp official account. Do not reply to anyone pretending to be Revolut or me. 

For the T&Cs and more details, head to the link in my bio #LightItUp
